<plot>An Army Special Ops officer posted in the Middle East returns home to visit his younger sister and finds her engaged to an anti-war activist. The men clash, as the war-weary officer also pursues a suspected female terrorist posing as a journalist. When the separate paths of the four characters converge, secrets are revealed, loves are lost and found, and finally, in climactic Capra-esque public showdown in which America's basic goodness is challenged and defended, lives are changed forever.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?553696</url></doc>
